<div class="bulk-format-card card mb-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between">
        <h2 class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-navy-900">
            {% include 'components/ui/icon.twig' with { name: 'ri-information-line', class: 'text-gold-600' } %}
            Format yang didukung
        </h2>
        <a href="/participants/bulk/template" class="btn-secondary inline-flex shrink-0 justify-center text-sm">
            {% include 'components/ui/icon.twig' with { name: 'ri-download-2-line', class: 'mr-1.5', size: 'sm' } %}
            Unduh Template CSV
        </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-navy-600">
        Kolom lengkap (disarankan): <strong>Nama, Rank, Gender, Telepon, GMS</strong>.
        Paste dari Excel/Google Sheets (tab otomatis) atau upload file CSV.
        Kolom Gender, Telepon, dan GMS boleh dikosongkan.
    </p>

    <ul class="bulk-format-list mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-navy-600">
        <li><strong>Header otomatis</strong> — baris pertama <code>Nama,Rank,Gender,Telepon,GMS</code> dikenali & dilewati</li>
        <li><strong>Format singkat</strong> — <code>Calvin,C</code> (rank wajib; gender/telp/GMS opsional)</li>
        <li><strong>No + Nama + Rank</strong> — <code>1,Calvin,C</code> (kolom nomor opsional)</li>
        <li><strong>Duplikat</strong> — nama yang sudah ada di daftar global (atau sudah di session) otomatis dilewati</li>
    </ul>

    <pre class="bulk-format-example mt-4">Nama,Rank,Gender,Telepon,GMS
Calvin,C,Male,081234567890,GMS
Yosua,B+,Female,081298765432,VIP
Pat,B,Male,,CP
Kevin,A-,Male,08111222333,PURI</pre>

    <div class="bulk-format-values mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-navy-50/50 p-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-navy-500">Rank</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-navy-700">{{ ranks|keys|join(', ') }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-navy-50/50 p-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-navy-500">Gender</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-navy-700">Male, Female, Other<br><span class="text-xs text-navy-500">Juga: M, F, Pria, Wanita</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-navy-50/50 p-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-navy-500">GMS</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-navy-700">{{ gmsSources|keys|join(', ') }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
